lorenz(x = x, y = cumsum(piketty.labor$Low))
text(x=c(0.3, 0.7, 0.95, 0.995), y=c(0.1, 0.3, 0.5, 0.6), labels=c("A", "B", "C", "D"), col="red")

A, B, C, D 2 2 A 2 (y[1] + y[2]) * (x[2] - x[1]), B 2 (y[2] + y[3])*(x[3] - x[2]), C 2 (y[3] + y[4]) * (x[4] - x[3]), D 2 (y[4] + y[5]) * (x[5] - x[4]) . x[1] y[1] 0 . x- . i- 2 (y[i] + y[i + 1])*(x[i + 1] - x[i]) . 1 .

.

gini
## function(x,y)
## {
##     n<-length(x)
##     i<-1:(n - 1)
##     s<-sum((y[i] + y[i + 1])*(x[i + 1] - x[i]))
##     s<-1 - s
##     return(s)
## }
